h3. Summary
When configuring the SLA, adding the Comment: For Customer in the Stop is causing the SLA to not show up in the Issue View.

h3. How to replicate
# Go to Service Desk Project configuration
# Click on SLA's
# Click on *New Metric* to create a new SLA
# Add Comment: For Customer in stop
# Enter 1h goal
# Click on Save

h3. Actual Behaviour
The SLA that contains Comment: For Customer in stop will be disappeared in some of issues

h3. Expected Behaviour
The SLA is working and appearing in the issue view as expected

